properties.areaDesc: Eastern Sierra Slopes of Inyo County
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 29 at 4:18AM PST until March 1 at 12:00AM PST by NWS Las Vegas NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Eastern Sierra Slopes.

* WHEN...From 4 PM this afternoon to midnight PST tonight.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO MIDNIGHT PST TONIGHT
